## Africana Studies Relation

**Africana Studies Relation:**  
Sammy Davis Jr. stands as an important figure within Africana Studies due to his contributions to the racial integration of the entertainment industry and his role in the Civil Rights Movement. His experiences highlight the intersections of race, entertainment, and activism in 20th-century America.

